ondor, must embrace his destiny and rally the kingdoms of Men to stand against the tide of evil. The elven archer Legolas, the dwarf warrior Gimli, and the wizard Gandalf all play crucial roles in the final battle against the shadow of Mordor.  With breathtaking landscapes, unforgettable characters, and epic battles, The Return of the King is a literary masterpiece that explores themes of courage, friendship, and the enduring struggle between good and evil. Tolkien\'s rich storytelling and intricate world-building come to a breathtaking crescendo in this thrilling and emotionally resonant conclusion to one of the greatest fantasy sagas ever told.'),('LORD OF THE RINGS: THE FELLOWSHIP OF THE RINGS','J.R.R. TOLKIEN','ENGLISH','[\"FANTASY\", \"ADVENTURE\", \"FICTION\"]','LORD OF THE RINGS',1,543,'LORD_OF_THE_RINGS_THE_FELLOWSHIP_OF_THE_RINGS_J.R.R._TOLKIEN.png','1954-07-29',NULL),('LORD OF THE RINGS: THE TWO TOWERS','J.R.R. TOLKIEN','ENGLISH','[\"ADVENTURE\", \"FANTASY\", \"FICTION\"]','LORD OF THE RINGS',2,801,'LORD_OF_THE_RINGS_THE_TWO_TOWERS_J.R.R._TOLKIEN.png','1954-11-11',NULL),('MACBETH','WILLIAM SHAKESPEARE','ENGLISH','[\"PLAY\", \"TRAGEDY\", \"FICTION\"]',NULL,NULL,682,'MACBETH_WILLIAM_SHAKESPEARE.png','1623-01-01',NULL),('MAHABHARAT','VED VYAS','SANSKRIT','[\"MYTHOLOGY\", \"EPIC\"]',NULL,NULL,728,'MAHABHARAT_VED_VYAS.png','0001-01-01',NULL),('MERCHANT OF VENICE','WILLIAM SHAKESPEARE','ENGLISH','[\"PLAY\", \"COMEDY\", \"FICTION\"]',NULL,NULL,659,'MERCHANT_OF_VENICE_WILLIAM_SHAKESPEARE.png','1598-07-22',NULL),('MOBY DICK','HERMAN MELVILLE','ENGLISH','[\"ADVENTURE\", \"FICTION\"]',NULL,NULL,1201,'MOBY_DICK_HERMAN_MELVILLE.png','1851-10-18',NULL),('MURDER ON THE ORIENT EXPRESS','AGATHA CHRISTIE','ENGLISH','[\"DETECTIVE\", \"MYSTERY\", \"FICTION\"]','HERCULE POIROT',10,1461,'MURDER_ON_THE_ORIENT_EXPRESS_AGATHA_CHRISTIE.png','1934-01-01','In Murder on the Orient Express, Agatha Christie\'s classic mystery novel, the legendary detective Hercule Poirot finds himself e